{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a case in a gas station where the Lithuanians have been drinking for a long time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they assembled a group of about 25 Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Within them was my teacher of mine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put in hoses, in their mouth, and they just-- I mean, they-- they poured gasoline and-- and water through their system, and-- and they just killed them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In way-- It was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The prisons were also filled up with so-called Communists and and Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was, truthfully-- to get over this short period of time and-- and to still be alive was actually a miracle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the next befehl [BACKROUND NOISE] was that the Jews have to assemble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They have to take their belongings, and-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] and they have to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they have to get assigned a place in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was also very difficult to find horses and the-- and wagons in order to transport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it took us some time in order to be able to get somebody that would do that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to pay him a much higher price, you know, for that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And finally, we had-- we were able and we felt that we are going to be more secure in the ghetto, because at least it's fenced around.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, of course, we didn't envision what is going to come afterward.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at least we felt that the the Lithuanians would not have a-- a easy way to come in and to murder the Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally we came to-- and we were able to get in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
